texts.content: {"text":"3. Ular namozni to`kis ado etadigan, \nzakotni beradigan va oxiratga qattiq ishonadiganlardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,93]}]}

{"text":"4. Albatta, oxiratga iymon keltirmaydiganlarga Biz amallarini ziynatlab ko`rsatdik. \nBas, ular adashib-uloqib yuraveradilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,124]}]}

{"text":"5. Ana o`shalarga yomon azob bordir va \nular oxiratda eng ko`p ziyon ko`rguvchilardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,86]}]}

{"text":"6. Albatta, senga bu Qur'on o`ta hikmatli va \no`ta ilmli Zot tomonidan berilur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"7. Muso o`z ahliga: Aniqki, men bir olov ko`rdim. Tezda men sizlarga undan biror xabar yoki isinishingiz uchun bir tutam cho`g` keltirurman, deganini esla.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,157]}]}

{"text":"8. U(olov)ga kelganida, \nolov oldidagi va atrofidagi shaxslarga baraka berildi va Olamlarning Robbi  Alloh pokdir, deb nido qilindi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,135]}]}

{"text":"9. Ey Muso! Albatta, bu  Menman! \nAziyzu hakiym Allohman!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"10. Va asoingni tashla! 
Bas, qachonki, Muso u(aso)ning 
ilondek qimirlayotganini ko`rganida, 
ortiga qaramay qochdi. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,119]}]}

{"text":"11. Lekin kim zulm qilsa-yu, so`ngra yomonlik ketidan unga yaxshilikni badal qilsa, bas, \nMen, albatta, mag`firatli va mehribondirman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,134]}]}

{"text":"12. Qo`lingni yoqangning ichiga suq, hech qanday yomonliksiz oppoq bo`lib chiqur. Fir'avn va uning qavmiga qaratilgan to`qqiz mo`jiza orasida \n(bu bordir). Albatta, ular buzg`unchi qavm bo`ldilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,196]}]}

{"text":"13. Bas, qachonki ularga oyat-mo`jizalarimiz \nko`z ochguvchi bo`lib kelganida, \nBu ochiq-oydin sehrdir, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,114]}]}

{"text":"14. Va o`zlari aniq bilib turib, zulm va kibr tufayli \nu(mo`jiza)larni inkor etdilar. Buzg`unchilarning oqibati qanday bo`lishiga nazar sol.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"15. Batahqiq, \nBiz Dovud va Sulaymonga ilm berdik. Ikkovlari: \nBizni ko`pgina mo`min bandalaridan afzal qilgan Allohga hamdlar bo`lsin, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,146]}]}

{"text":"16. Va Sulaymon Dovudga voris bo`ldi. 
U: Ey odamlar, bizga qush tili o`rgatildi 
va har bir narsadan berildi. 
Bu, albatta, ochiq-oydin fazldir, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,153]}]}

{"text":"17. Sulaymonga jin, ins va qushlardan bo`lgan askarlari to`planib, tizilgan holda turdilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,91]}]}

{"text":"18. Toki ular chumolilar vodiysiga kelganlarida, \nbir chumoli: Ey, chumolilar, maskanlaringga kiringlar, Sulaymon va uning askarlari sizlarni bilmasdan ezib yubormasinlar, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,179]}]}

{"text":"19. Bas, u uning so`zidan tabassum qildi va: \nRobbim, meni O`zing menga va ota-onamga bergan ne'matlaringga shukr etishimga va Sen rozi bo`ladigan solih amallar qilishimga muyassar etgin. O`z rahmating ila meni solih bandalaringga qo`shgin, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,248]}]}

{"text":"20. Va qushlarni tekshirdi-da: Nega Hudhudni \nko`rmayotirman yoki g`oyiblardan bo`ldimi? dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,96]}]}

{"text":"21. Albatta, uni shiddatli azob-la azoblarman yoki so`yib yuborurman yoxud menga, albatta, ochiq-oydin hujjat keltirajak.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,123]}]}

{"text":"22. Ko`p o`tmasdan u kelib: \nSen bilmagan narsani bildim va senga \nSaba'dan ishonchli bir xabar olib keldim.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,109]}]}

{"text":"23. Darhaqiqat, men bir ayolni ko`rdim. 
U ularning malikasi ekan. 
Unga har narsa berilgan ekan. 
Hamda uning ulug` taxti bor ekan.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,132]}]}

{"text":"24. Men u(ayol)ning va qavmining Allohni qo`yib, quyoshga sajda qilayotganlarini va 
shayton ularga amallarini ziynatlab, 
yo`ldan to`sayotganini ko`rdim. 
Bas, ular hidoyat topmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,184]}]}

{"text":"25. Osmonlaru yerdagi sirlarni oshkor qiladigan, maxfiy va oshkor qilgan narsalaringizni biladigan Allohga sajda qilmaydilarmi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,128]}]}

{"text":"26. Alloh  Undan o`zga hech qanday iloh yo`q Zotdir. U ulug` arshning Robbidir, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,87]}]}

{"text":"28. Bu maktubimni olib borib, ularga tashla, \nso`ngra chetga chiqib nazar sol-chi, \nnima qaytarurlar, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,108]}]}

{"text":"29. U (Malika): Ey, a'yonlar! \nMenga karomatli bir maktub tashlandi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"30. Albatta, u Sulaymondandir, albatta, \nunda: Bismillahir rohmanir rohiym.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"31. Menga qarshi bosh ko`tarmay, \ntaslim bo`lgan holingizda keling, deyilmishdir, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"32. U (Malika): Ey, a'yonlar! \nMenga bu ishimda fatvo (maslahat) beringlar. Sizlar shohid bo`lmaguningizcha, \nmen bir ishga qat'iy qaror qilmasman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,155]}]}

{"text":"33. Ular: Biz kuch-quvvat egalarimiz va shiddatli azmu shijoat egalarimiz. Ish o`zingga havola. Nima amr qilishingni o`ylab ko`r, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"34. U: Albatta, podshohlar biror shahar-qishloqqa kirsalar, uni vayron qilurlar va uning aziz ahllarini xor qilurlar. Ana shunday qilurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"35. Men ularga bir hadya yuborurman, \nko`ray-chi, elchilar nima bilan qaytar ekanlar, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,92]}]}

{"text":"36. Qachonki, (elchisi) Sulaymonga kelganida, u: \nSizlar menga mol-dunyo ila madad bermoqchimisiz?! Bas, Alloh menga bergan narsa sizga bergan narsadan yaxshidir. Ammo sizlar hadyalaringiz \nbilan quvonursiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,208]}]}

{"text":"37. (Ey elchi!) Sen ularga qaytib bor. \nBas, albatta, biz ular bas kela olmaydigan \nqo`shin ila borurmiz va u yerdan ularni xoru zor hollarida chiqarurmiz, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,162]}]}

{"text":"38. U (Sulaymon): Ey a'yonlar! \nUlar menga taslim bo`lib kelishlaridan oldin qaysingiz huzurimga u(malika)ning taxtini \nkeltira oladi? dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,142]}]}

{"text":"39. Jinlardan bo`lgan Ifrit: \nMen uni senga maqomingdan turguningcha keltirurman. Albatta, bunga quvvatim va \nishonchim bor, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,132]}]}

{"text":"40. Kitobdan ilmi bor shaxs: Men uni senga \nko`zingni ochib yumguningcha keltirurman, dedi. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,94]}]}

{"text":"Qachonki (Sulaymon) u(taxt)ning o`z \nhuzurida qaror topganini ko`rgach: \nBu Robbimning fazlidandir. Men shukr qilamanmi yoki kufroni ne'mat qilamanmi, sinash uchundir. Kim shukr keltirsa, o`zi uchungina shukr qilur. Kim kufroni ne'mat qilsa, bas, Robbim behojat va karamli Zotdir, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,288]}]}

{"text":"41. U (Sulaymon): Uning taxtini tanimaydigan qilib qo`ying. Ko`raylik-chi, u(malika) uni tanirmi yoki tanimaydiganlardan bo`lurmi? dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,138]}]}

{"text":"42. Qachonki u kelganida: Sening taxting shundaymi? deyildi. U: Xuddi o`shaning o`zi, dedi. Bizga bundan ilgari ilm berilgan edi va musulmon bo`lgan edik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,160]}]}

{"text":"43. Va u(malika)ni Allohdan \no`zga ibodat qilgan narsa to`sdi. \nAlbatta, u kofir qavmlardan bo`lgan edi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,104]}]}

{"text":"44. U(malika)ga: Saroyga kir, deyildi. \nQachonki uni ko`rganida, suv deb o`ylab, poychalarini ochdi. U(Sulaymon): Albatta, \nbu billurdan silliq qilib yasalgan saroydir, dedi. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,179]}]}

{"text":"U(malika): Ey Robbim, albatta, \nmen o`zimga zulm qilib yurgan ekanman, Sulaymon ila olamlarning Robbi  \nAllohga musulmon bo`ldim! dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,138]}]}

{"text":"45. Batahqiq, 
Samud qavmiga, Allohga ibodat qiling, 
deb birodarlari Solihni yubordik. 
Bas, banogoh, ular ikki guruh bo`lib tortisha boshladilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,147]}]}

{"text":"46. U (Solih): Ey qavmim, nima uchun yaxshilikdan oldin yomonlikka oshiqasiz?! Allohdan mag`firat so`rasangiz-chi?! \nShoyad rahim qilinsangiz, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,150]}]}

{"text":"47. Ular: Sendan va sen bilan 
bo`lganlardan shumlandik, dedilar. 
U: Shumlanishingiz Allohning huzuridadir. 
Balki sizlar sinalayotgan qavmsiz, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,154]}]}

{"text":"48. U shaharda to`qqiz nafarli guruh bor bo`lib, yer yuzida buzg`unchilik qilishar, isloh qilmas edilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,104]}]}

{"text":"49. Ular: Allohning nomiga qasam ichinglar! \nAlbatta, u (Solih)ni va uning ahlini tunda o`ldiramiz, \nso`ngra valiyiga, biz uning ahlining halokatiga guvoh emasmiz, albatta, biz rostgo`ylarmiz, deymiz, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,211]}]}

{"text":"50. Ular makr qildilar. \nBiz ham ular sezmagan holda bir makr qildik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,71]}]}

{"text":"51. Nazar sol! Ularning makri oqibati nima bo`ldi?! Biz, albatta, ularni va qavmlarini, hammalarini yer bilan yakson qildik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,124]}]}

{"text":"52. Ana, zulmlari sababli uylari huvillab yotibdi! Albatta, bunda biladigan qavmlar uchun ibrat bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,103]}]}

{"text":"53. Va iymon keltirib, \ntaqvo qilib yurganlarga najot berdik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"54. Va Lutni ham (Payg`ambar qilib yubordik). \nO`shanda u o`z qavmiga: Siz ko`rib-bilib turib, fohisha ish qilasizmi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,119]}]}

{"text":"55. Siz, albatta, ayollarni qo`yib, \nerkaklarga shahvat ila yaqinlik qilasizmi?! \nYo`q! Siz johillik qilayotgan qavmdirsiz! dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,130]}]}

{"text":"56. Uning qavmining javobi: \nLut ahlini yurtingizdan quvib chiqaring, \nchunki ular pokiza bo`lishni xohlagan kishilardir, deyishdan boshqa narsa bo`lmadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,156]}]}

{"text":"57. Bas, Biz unga va xotinidan boshqa ahliga najot berdik. U(xotin)ning azobda qolguvchilar ichida bo`lishini taqdir qildik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,124]}]}

{"text":"58. Va ularning ustlariga bir yomg`ir yog`dirdikki, bas, ogohlantirilganlarning azobi qanday ham yomon bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,110]}]}

{"text":"59. Sen: Allohga hamd bo`lsin va U tanlab olgan bandalariga salom bo`lsin. Alloh yaxshimi yoki ular shirk keltirayotgan narsalarmi? degin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"60. Yoki osmonlaru yerni yaratgan, 
sizlarga osmondan suv tushirgan Zotmi? 
Bas, Biz u(suv) bilan go`zal bog`lar o`stirdik. 
Siz o`zingiz uning daraxtini o`stira olmas edingiz. Alloh bilan birga boshqa iloh bormi?! ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,215]}]}
